extendedInfo.description: **Free Version only has access to first ten documents* This is the Ultimate Survival guide. This Apocalypse App has over 1,000 documents from building shelters,identifying edible plants, surviving in the desert to nuclear fall out shelters. Be ready in the case of an emergency like CPR or basic life saving medical bits. You can learn a lot from this App!
